name: Holly Kennedy
description: “People think that a soul mate is a person with whom you fit perfectly, which is what everyone wants. But a true soul mate is a mirror, it is the person who brings up all that you have repressed, which makes you look inward recognizing that you can change your life. A true soul mate is certainly the most important person you have ever met in your life. But should we live with a soul mate forever? No way. We will live very badly. The soul mate enters your life, takes the veil out of your eyes and goes away ”
